thread.section_title: buyMyplace Reviews | Customer Service Reviews of buyMyplace | www.buymyplace.com.au
thread.title: Warren

author: Warren
title: Warren
text:
Great way to sell a house. Saves you heaps of Money.
Only thing I would complain about was that because we were in Perth, there was a bit of miscommunication at times.
e.g. They organised a Photographer to attend, but he was given an address in Queensland. Also, the lady who wrote the description was given the wrong State.
Small things that were quickly sorted, so just make sure details are correct and confirm with everything when booking Photographer etc.
Apart from that service was great although at times was a bit hard to get hold of them.
